title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
OB: When calling the stored procedure from the Oracle database, the query result that is stored in the output parameter does not display in the data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog to see if the output parameter is displayed.
